children.subject: Has anyone heard back from this?

history.content:
Join Jane Street and UPE on March 1st @ 6pm PT for an in-person Estimathon™!

The Estimathon™ is a mind-bending mixture of math and trivia. In teams, you'll attempt 13 Fermi problems in 30 minutes, ranging from totally trivial to positively Putnamesque. Be prepared to come up with the best set of confidence intervals!

Please signup by SUNDAY, FEBRUARY 27th @ 11:59pm PT if you're interested in attending. Jane Street will confirm attendees via email by MONDAY, FEBRUARY 28 @ 5pm - hope to see you there!

Sign Up Here: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfSBjFs2inXdij_xZecFkj8t1A8VEMr3kRDkTV82H8zK7pXYQ/viewform

COVID Policies: All participants MUST be fully vaccinated in order to attend. For the purposes of this event, fully vaccinated means 6 weeks after the single dose J&J, 3 weeks after the second dose of Pfizer, and 2 weeks after the second dose of Moderna. This event will be indoors, so masks will be required.
